
1. Inversion Of Control: 

					Object Factory ---> config  --> Object is created
					Spring Container will create and Manage the Objects.
					Inject Object Dependencies.

					Configuration:
						1. XML
						2. Java Annotation
						3. Java Source Code(modern)
						
			1. XML
					Add a Config file in src
					Create Object of ClassPathXmlApplicationContext and pass config file
					load the bean using bean name and class type.
						Coach c=context.getBean("myCoach",Coach.class);

			Dependency Injection: Helper Objects
				MyApp-----Spring[Object Factory]---config------Any Object

					1. Construction Injection
							
					2. Setter Injection